Description

 
Questor is a secret-riddled 2D Platformer where you must maneuver through challenging levels and face difficult enemies!

Features

With Three extensive levels, each one harder than the last, this game will keep you occupied for a while(10 Minutes)...


Exciting Powerups!



The ability to Double Jump!



Development Log
